{"about_the_game":"In 1592, Japan invaded the Joseon on Korean Peninsula, initiating the Imjin War. <br>Despite eventually repelling the Japanese forces after a long and arduous conflict, Joseon fell into disarray due to the aftermath of the war. <br>Bandits emerged across the land, and corrupt officials exploited the chaos to plunder the people.<br><br><strong>In an effort to rectify this situation, an unnamed Seonbi embarked on the path.</strong><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/action1.gif?t=1726530236\" /><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is a side-scrolling action game developed with the historical backdrop of Korea. <br>As a player, you will encounter bandits, remnants of the Japanese forces, and monsters on your journey.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/action4.gif?t=1726530236\" /><br>Using a bow as your primary weapon and a variety of skills and items inspired by the weaponry of the Joseon era, you must strategically utilize them to defeat enemies and reach Hanyang (modern-day Seoul).<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/action3.gif?t=1726530236\" /><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is designed to fluidly connect short actions, enabling players to string together combos and experience the thrill of direct combat.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/action2.gif?t=1726530236\" /><br>Equip yourself with your unique skills and item combinations, assist the citizens in dire situations, and journey to Hanyang to rectify the chaos that plagues Joseon!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Game Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1925860/b73efc5e703d7b786a2568e7ba3c76a